Cerminan Hati di belakang gunung

245
00:22:55,959 --> 00:22:57,439
dan bertaubat selama 20 hari.

246
00:22:58,040 --> 00:22:59,439
Ya, tok guru.

247
00:23:09,760 --> 00:23:11,640
Tok guru, 20 hari

248
00:23:11,839 --> 00:23:12,959
dah terlalu lama.

249
00:23:13,280 --> 00:23:14,239
Kali ini,

250
00:23:14,800 --> 00:23:16,439
tiada orang boleh memihak kepada dia.

251
00:23:17,880 --> 00:23:20,199
Saya mahu dia ingat pengajaran ini.

252
00:23:22,800 --> 00:23:23,599
Qing Yan,

253
00:23:24,040 --> 00:23:24,839
jangan susah hati.

254
00:23:25,160 --> 00:23:26,880
Dua puluh hari berlalu dengan cepat.

255
00:23:28,959 --> 00:23:30,479
Terima kasih, Abang Qing Feng.

256
00:23:32,079 --> 00:23:33,920
(Tiada pelindung berjampi
di gunung belakang,)

257
00:23:34,239 --> 00:23:36,199
