303
00:26:42,239 --> 00:26:45,000
Dengar sini, gadis ini kawan baik saya.

304
00:26:45,319 --> 00:26:46,880
Bolehkah kamu berikan muka kepada saya

305
00:26:47,040 --> 00:26:48,160
dan lepaskan dia?

306
00:26:49,040 --> 00:26:50,880
Gadis? Dia jin burung!

307
00:26:51,040 --> 00:26:51,719
Awak...

308
00:26:52,400 --> 00:26:54,920
Awak ada aura dewa,

309
00:26:55,160 --> 00:26:56,439
pastinya dewa Suku Langit.

310
00:26:56,800 --> 00:26:58,439
Kenapa awak nak menyebelahi jin burung?

311
00:27:00,160 --> 00:27:02,400
Walaupun dia jin burung,
dia bertapa secara ikhlas.

312
00:27:02,560 --> 00:27:04,160
Dia pasti boleh jadi dewi lama-kelamaan.

313
00:27:04,319 --> 00:27:05,079
Jangan ingat

314
00:27:05,079 --> 00:27:06,400
dewa boleh bertindak sembarangan.

315
00:27:07,000 --> 00:27:08,199
Sekta Kunlun membunuh syaitan dan jin

316
00:27:08,199 --> 00:27:09,319
demi keadilan.

317
00:27:09,599 --> 00:27:11,479
Kalau awak menghalang manusia
membunuh syaitan,

318
00:27:11,760 --> 00:27:12,760
maksudnya, awak dah melanggar
Undang-undang Dewa.

319
00:27:12,920 --> 00:27:14,160
Awak...

320
00:27:14,359 --> 00:27:15,680
Awak nampak?

321
00:27:15,839 --> 00:27:17,280
Pengikut Sekta Kunlun

322
00:27:17,439 --> 00:27:18,359
memang tak munasabah.

323
00:27:18,560 --> 00:27:20,119
Jin burung ini amat misteri

324
00:27:20,119 --> 00:27:21,280
kerana memasuki kawasan Sekta Kunlun.

325
00:27:21,719 --> 00:27:22,880
Kalau tak bunuh dia sekarang juga,

326
00:27:23,199 --> 00:27:25,119
dah terlewat apabila malapetaka wujud!

327
00:27:29,000 --> 00:27:30,280
Kalau saya guna kuasa sihir
di alam manusia,

328
00:27:30,439 --> 00:27:31,839
maka, saya akan melanggar
Undang-undang Dewa.

329
00:27:32,040 --> 00:27:33,319
Saya masih boleh berlawan dengan kamu

330
00:27:33,439 --> 00:27:34,719
tanpa guna kuasa sihir.

331
00:27:35,479 --> 00:27:37,479
Hari ini, saya mesti bawa dia pergi.

332
00:29:02,479 --> 00:29:03,400
Berhati-hati!

333
00:29:33,719 --> 00:29:34,599
Jangan!

334
00:29:38,599 --> 00:29:39,520
Xiao Qing!

335
00:30:16,439 --> 00:30:17,959
Rupa-rupanya, parut ini

336
00:30:19,199 --> 00:30:21,040
disambar petir samawi.

337
00:30:21,479 --> 00:30:22,800
Awak dah ingat semula?

338
00:30:33,119 --> 00:30:34,520
Beberapa gambaran

339
00:30:34,680 --> 00:30:36,520
muncul dalam fikiran saya.

340
00:30:37,400 --> 00:30:38,319
Adakah

341
00:30:39,680 --> 00:30:41,920
kita berkenalan sejak 1000 tahun lalu?

342
00:30:58,319 --> 00:30:59,199
Ya.

343
00:32:10,800 --> 00:32:14,359
Burung Xuan Biru mengumpan
Bintang Sepi keabaian tugas.

344
00:32:15,199 --> 00:32:17,040
Kamu berdua mengaku kesalahan?

345
00:32:51,239 --> 00:32:56,319
♪Mimpi tak dapat dipegang,
maka lahirnya nostalgia♪

346
00:32:56,399 --> 00:33:01,639
